Enhance UI design and functionality
Enhance and optimize the Sketchlab application with new features and improvements.
* **UI Design and Responsiveness** - Update `docs/app/(home)/page.tsx` to have a minimalist, modern, and sleek design. - Apply consistent typography styles and ensure responsive design using Tailwind CSS utility classes. - Add custom theme variables, typography styles, and responsive typography in `docs/app/global.css`. - Import `tw-animate-css` library for smooth transitions and animations. - Define dark mode color variables.
* **Component Enhancements** - Apply Tailwind CSS utility classes for styling and responsive design in `docs/components/ui/button.tsx` and `docs/components/ui/card.tsx`. - Use `lucide-react` icons and implement smooth transitions and animations in `docs/components/ui/dialog.tsx` and `docs/components/ui/dropdown-menu.tsx`.
* **Preview Component** - Optimize iframe reloading with a debounce mechanism and improve error handling in `src/components/Preview.tsx`. - Support SVG generation using `p5-svg.js` and include an export button.
* **Plugin Manager** - Enhance plugin management UI with search, filter, categories, ratings, and reviews in `src/components/PluginManager.tsx`.
* **Settings Component** - Add user preference options for theme selection, font size, image format, and image resolution in `src/components/Settings.tsx`. - Save user preferences to local storage and load them on component mount. - Provide a reset option to reset user preferences to default values.
* **Editor Component** - Optimize editor initialization with a debounce mechanism and improve error handling in `src/components/Editor.tsx`.
* **Documentation** - Update `docs/api-guide.md` and `README.md` to include information about the new SVG generation functionality.
